headline: Lennox Declares Quarterly Dividend and Announces Annual Meeting
summary: The Lennox board of directors (NYSE: LII) approved a quarterly cash dividend of $1.30 per share of common stock, payable January 15, 2026, to stockholders of record as of December 31, 2025.
